      "content": "idk i just feel so nauseous and the light is really bothering me... feels a lot like when i get migraines. do you think maybe it's just a cluster headache or a bad migraine flare up? i dont really want to go to the er if i can help it, it's so expensive and the wait is always hours and hours. is there anything else i can take to make the drooping go away faster?",
